@startuml SaniHub-BPMN-OrderToCash
title SaniHub — BPMN : Processus Order-to-Cash

participant "Client B2B\n(EDI)" as Client
participant "TrueCommerce" as TC
participant "SaniHub Hub" as Hub
participant "Infor M3" as M3
participant "Ortems" as Ortems
participant "BBX\n(Warehouse)" as BBX
participant "Expédition" as Ship

== Phase 1 : Réception Commande ==
Client ->> TC: Envoie EDI 850 (commande)
activate TC
TC ->> TC: Parse EDI, valide formatzzzz
TC ->> Hub: POST /events/publish\n{CommandeClientRecue}
deactivate TC

== Phase 2 : Centralisation & Routage ==
activate Hub
Hub ->> Hub: Route decision:\nCommandeClientRecue → Canonical
Hub ->> Hub: Transform: TrueCommerce → CommandeClient
Hub ->> Hub: Routine policy:\n[M3, Ortems, Dynamics]
Hub -->> TC: 200 Accepted (message_id: MSG-123)
deactivate Hub

== Phase 3 : Notification à M3 ==
Hub ->> M3: Event: CommandeClientCree (canonical)
activate M3
M3 ->> M3: M3 Connecteur reçoit\nTransform: Canonical → Format M3
M3 ->> M3: Crée order, valide stock
M3 -->> Hub: Event: CommandeM3Created\n+ M3_OrderId
deactivate M3

== Phase 4 : Notification à Ortems ==
Hub ->> Ortems: Event: CommandeClientCree (canonical)
activate Ortems
Ortems ->> Ortems: Ortems Connecteur reçoit\nTransform: Canonical → Format Ortems
Ortems ->> Ortems: Crée ODF (Ordre Fabrication)\nRéserve ressources
note over Ortems: Parallel execution\nwith M3
Ortems -->> Hub: Event: OdfCreated\n+ Ortems_OdfId
deactivate Ortems

== Phase 5 : Génération Picklist ==
Hub ->> BBX: Event: OdfCreated\n(ou Picklist.Generate)
activate BBX
BBX ->> BBX: Génère picklist\nRéserve articles warehouse
BBX -->> Hub: Event: PicklistGenerated\n+ picklist_id
deactivate BBX

== Phase 6 : Fulfilment & Expédition ==
parallel
    BBX ->> Ortems: Je suis prêt à picker
    Ortems ->> Ortems: Confirme disponibilité ressources, ordonne picking
    BBX ->> BBX: Picking + packing + labeling
end

== Phase 7 : Statut Expédition ==
BBX ->> Hub: Event: ExpeditionPreparee\n+ shipping_number, tracking_url
activate Hub
Hub ->> Hub: Route to: [TrueCommerce, Dynamics, M3]
Hub -->> BBX: 200 OK
deactivate Hub

== Phase 8 : Confirmation B2B ==
Hub ->> TC: Event: ExpeditionPreparee
activate TC
TC ->> TC: Connecteur adapte → EDI 856 (Shipment Notice)
TC ->> Client: Envoie EDI 856 au client (avec tracking)
note over Client: Client receives shipment notice
deactivate TC

== Phase 9 : Clôture Commande ==
Hub ->> M3: Event: ExpeditionPreparee
activate M3
M3 ->> M3: Ferme order, statut = Shipped
M3 -->> Hub: Event: CommandeFinalisee
deactivate M3

== Traçabilité ==
note over Hub
Chaque événement contient:
- correlation_id = CMD-12345 (commande origin)
- timestamp, source_app, target_apps
- status (Published → Routed → Delivered)

Dashboard SaniHub peut répondre "Où est la commande 12345 ?":
1. ✓ TrueCommerce.CommandeClientRecue (10:53:01)
2. ✓ Hub.CommandeClientCree (10:53:02)
3. ✓ M3.CommandeM3Created (10:53:05, M3-87654)
4. ✓ Ortems.OdfCreated (10:53:06, ODF-555)
5. ✓ BBX.PicklistGenerated (10:53:30, PL-999)
6. ✓ BBX.ExpeditionPreparee (11:45:00, TRK-ABC123)
7. ✓ TC.EDI856Sent (11:45:15)
8. ✓ M3.CommandeFinalisee (11:45:30)
end note

@enduml

