@startuml SaniHub-BPMN-ProducureToPay
title SaniHub — BPMN : Processus Procure-to-Pay

participant "M3\n(Planning)" as M3
participant "SaniHub Hub" as Hub
participant "Ortems" as Ortems
participant "BBX" as BBX
participant "External\nSupplier" as Supplier
participant "Dynamics 365\n(Finance)" as D365

== Phase 1 : Planification Besoins ==
M3 ->> M3: M3 Planification crée besoins\n(Stock seuil atteint, production needs)
M3 ->> Hub: Event: BesoinsCreationDemandee\n{article, qty, dateLivraison}
activate Hub

== Phase 2 : Création Commande Achat ==
Hub ->> Hub: Route: BesoinsCreationDemandee → EnrichedPO
Hub ->> Hub: Enrichit avec données fournisseur\n(best supplier, prix catalogue)
Hub ->> Hub: Transform: canonical → CommandeAchat
Hub -->> M3: 200 Accepted
deactivate Hub

== Phase 3 : Envoi Fournisseur ==
Hub ->> Supplier: Event: CommandeAchat\n(EDI 850 ou email/API)
activate Supplier
note over Supplier: External supplier\nReceives PO (asynchrone)
Supplier ->> Supplier: Supplier confirms reception
Supplier -->> Hub: Event: PoConfirmed\n(tracking, delivery date)
deactivate Supplier

== Phase 4 : Livraison Marchandise ==
Supplier ->> Supplier: Prépare shipment
Supplier ->> BBX: Envoie colis
activate BBX
BBX ->> BBX: Reçoit marchandise\nscanne barcodes
BBX ->> Hub: Event: ReceptionMarchandiseConfirmee\n{article, qty_recu, date_reception}
deactivate BBX

== Phase 5 : Mise à Jour Stock ==
Hub ->> M3: Event: ReceptionMarchandiseConfirmee
activate M3
M3 ->> M3: M3 connecteur reçoit\nMet à jour stock, disponibilité
M3 -->> Hub: Event: StockMisAJour\n{article, qty_available}
deactivate M3

== Phase 6 : Facturation ==
Supplier ->> Supplier: Prépare facture
Supplier ->> D365: Envoie facture (email, API, EDI 810)
activate D365
D365 ->> Hub: Event: FactureRecue\n{po_id, qty_facture, montant, due_date}

== Phase 7 : Reconciliation Finance ==
Hub ->> D365: Event: ReceptionMarchandiseConfirmee\n(2-way matching: PO ↔ Goods ↔ Invoice)
note over D365: 3-way matching workflow\nPO ↔ Goods Receipt ↔ Invoice
D365 ->> D365: Valide: qty et montant OK?\nPas d'écart
D365 -->> Hub: Event: FactureValidee\nStatus: Ready for payment

== Phase 8 : Paiement ==
D365 ->> D365: Crée payment instruction\nSchedule payment date
D365 -->> Supplier: Wire transfer / Payment (external system)

== Traçabilité ==
note over Hub
Chaque événement contient:
- correlation_id = PO-67890 (purchase order origin)
- timestamp, source_app, target_apps

Dashboard SaniHub pour "État de la PO 67890 ?":
1. ✓ M3.BesoinsCreationDemandee (2026-04-13 14:00)
2. ✓ Hub.CommandeAchatCree (2026-04-13 14:01)
3. ✓ Supplier.PoConfirmed (2026-04-14 09:30)
4. ✓ BBX.ReceptionMarhandiseConfirmee (2026-04-20 10:15)
5. ✓ M3.StockMisAJour (2026-04-20 10:35)
6. ✓ D365.FactureRecue (2026-04-21 08:00)
7. ✓ D365.FactureValidee (2026-04-21 11:00, ready for payment)
8. ✓ D365.PaymentProcessed (2026-04-28 EOD)
end note

@enduml

