@startuml SaniHub-Event-Error-Handling
title SaniHub — Scénario d'Erreur & Résilience

participant "App Métier\n(M3, Dynamics)" as App
participant "SaniHub\nAPI Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "Message\nBroker" as Broker
participant "Connecteur\nCible" as Connector
participant "App\nCible" as TargetApp
participant "Dead Letter\nQueue" as DLQ
participant "Dashboard\n& Alert" as Alert

== Scénario Normal ==
App ->> APIGateway: POST /events/publish\n{CommandeClientCree}
APIGateway ->> Broker: Publie event
Broker ->> Connector: Envoi event au connecteur
Connector ->> TargetApp: Écrit dans app cible
TargetApp -->> Connector: 200 OK

Connector ->> Broker: Publie event success\n{type: Delivered}
note over Broker: Success path✓

== Scénario d'Erreur Temporaire ==
Connector ->> TargetApp: Connecteur écrit vers app\n(Ortems API)
TargetApp -->> Connector: 503 Service Unavailable
note over Connector: Retry logic activé

Connector ->> Connector: Wait 1s, retry 1
Connector ->> TargetApp: Retry 1 (backoff exponential)
TargetApp -->> Connector: 503 Service Unavailable

Connector ->> Connector: Wait 2s, retry 2
Connector ->> TargetApp: Retry 2
TargetApp -->> Connector: 503 Service Unavailable

Connector ->> Connector: Wait 4s, retry 3
Connector ->> TargetApp: Retry 3
TargetApp -->> Connector: 200 OK
note over Connector: Eventual success ✓

Connector ->> Broker: Publie event EventuallyDelivered
alert_level = INFO (logged for monitoring)

== Scénario d'Erreur Permanente ==
Connector ->> TargetApp: Connecteur écrit\n(Ortems down, infrastructure issue)
TargetApp -->> Connector: Connection timeout

loop Retry 1/2/3 (with backoff)
    Connector ->> TargetApp: Retry (fail)
end

Connector ->> DLQ: Envoie event à Dead Letter Queue
note over DLQ: {event, error_reason, last_attempt_time}

Connector ->> Broker: Publie event Failed\n{type: DeliveryFailed, error: "Ortems::Timeout"}

Broker ->> Alert: Déclenche alerte\n(Severity: CRITICAL)
Alert ->> Alert: Slack/Email à équipe on-call\n"Ortems intégration down, 50 events in DLQ"

== Opérateur IT : Diagnostic & Replay ==
Alert ->> Dashboard: Opérateur ouvre dashboard\nVoit : "Ortems: DLQ = 50 events, last error = Connection timeout"

Dashboard ->> Dashboard: Opérateur investigate\nOrtems service status? Firewall? DB issues?

Note over Alert: Ortems équipe répond:\n"Infra maintenance terminée 15:30"

== Opérateur IT : Manual Replay ==
Dashboard ->> APIGateway: POST /admin/replay\n{correlation_ids: [CMD-12345, CMD-12346, ...], source: DLQ}

APIGateway ->> Broker: Ré-publie events from DLQ\n(avec flag: retry_from_dlq=true)

Broker ->> Connector: Re-envoi connecteur

Connector ->> TargetApp: Écrit à nouveau\n(Ortems maintenant en ligne)
TargetApp -->> Connector: 200 OK
note over Connector: Success ✓

Connector ->> Broker: Publie event Replayed\n{original_correlation_id, replayed_at}

Dashboard ->> Alert: Affiche: "Replay successful: 50/50 events delivered"
Alert -->> Alert: Alerte résolue, tickets fermés

@enduml
